---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Crypto & Web3 Advisory | ARM Management"
  description="VARA licence advisory, MiCA CASP authorisation, token structuring, DAO legal frameworks, and crypto company formation across major virtual asset jurisdictions."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639762681485-074b7f938ba0?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Crypto &amp; Web3</span>
      <h1>Crypto &amp; Web3 Advisory</h1>
      <p>VARA · MiCA · MAS · SFC · VASP licensing and regulatory strategy across major crypto jurisdictions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">What We Do</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Regulated Crypto Operations, Built Correctly.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">The regulatory environment for virtual assets and Web3 businesses has changed dramatically. The UAE's VARA framework, the EU's MiCA regulation, and licensing regimes in Singapore, Hong Kong, and other major jurisdictions have created clear pathways for compliant crypto operations — and equally clear consequences for those who operate without the correct licences.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">ARM Management advises exchanges, DeFi protocols, NFT platforms, token issuers, DAOs, and Web3 infrastructure businesses on regulatory strategy across major crypto jurisdictions. We combine legal structuring, regulatory advisory, and AML programme design into a single coordinated engagement.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Services</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What We Advise On</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>VARA Licence Advisory (Dubai)</h3>
          <p>End-to-end application support for all seven VARA activity categories including entity formation, AML/CFT programme design, business plan preparation, and regulatory liaison with VARA.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>MiCA Compliance (EU)</h3>
          <p>CASP authorisation across EU member states — Malta, Lithuania, Ireland, Netherlands, and others. Home member state selection, regulatory gap analysis, and NCA application management.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Token Structuring &amp; Legal Analysis</h3>
          <p>Token classification assessment under applicable regulatory frameworks, issuance structuring, whitepaper review, and legal opinion preparation for token launches and DeFi protocol design.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>DAO Legal Frameworks</h3>
          <p>Structuring decentralised autonomous organisations using Marshall Islands DAO LLC, Wyoming DAO LLC, or Cayman Foundation structures — providing legal personality without compromising decentralisation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Crypto Company Formation</h3>
          <p>Incorporation in optimal jurisdictions: DMCC Dubai, BVI, Cayman Islands, Malta, Singapore. Entity selection aligned with licensing requirements, operational needs, and banking access.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>AML/CFT Programme Design</h3>
          <p>KYC procedures, transaction monitoring frameworks, Travel Rule compliance, and suspicious activity reporting — designed to meet regulatory requirements and pass VASP due diligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">The ARM Approach</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">Regulation as a Competitive Advantage.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78)">Most Web3 businesses treat regulation as a constraint to be managed. The businesses that grow into institutional-grade operations treat it as a competitive advantage — a barrier to entry that separates credible operators from the rest. ARM Management works with clients who want to build lasting, licensable businesses. We advise honestly on which jurisdictions are genuinely achievable, what a licence will and will not allow, and what compliance infrastructure is required before any regulator will take an application seriously.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Jurisdiction Selection</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">The right licence jurisdiction depends on your business model, target markets, investor profile, and banking requirements. We assess all of these before recommending a path.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Regulatory Readiness</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">A licence application submitted before the business is ready wastes time and damages credibility with regulators. We assess readiness before filing and fix gaps first.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Banking Access</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Crypto businesses face persistent banking challenges. We advise on banking-compatible structures and maintain relationships with institutions that bank compliant VASPs.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Post-Licence Compliance</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Obtaining a licence is the beginning, not the end. We support ongoing compliance, regulatory reporting, AML programme maintenance, and licence condition management.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Where We Advise</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="reveal" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:32px">
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">UAE (VARA)</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">VARA Virtual Asset Service Provider licences across all seven activity categories. DMCC entity formation. Full VASP licensing.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">European Union (MiCA)</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">MiCA CASP authorisation across Malta, Lithuania, Ireland, and the Netherlands. MICA-compliant token issuance advisory.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Singapore &amp; Hong Kong</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">MAS regulatory advisory and MPI licence support for Singapore. SFC VASP licensing guidance for Hong Kong.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Offshore Structures</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">BVI, Cayman Islands, Marshall Islands, and Wyoming for token issuance, DAO structures, and holding entities.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Discuss Your Crypto Regulatory Strategy</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Tell us what your business does, which markets you serve, and where you want to be licensed. We will give you an honest assessment of what is achievable, on what timeline, and at what cost.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/insights" class="btn-secondary">Read Our Insights</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
